<h1>About Eleni's Healthy Habits</h1>

<div class="about-container">
    <div class="intro-section">
      @*   <img src="path-to-your-image.jpg" alt="Eleni" class="profile-image" /> *@
        <h2>Welcome to Eleni's Healthy Habits!</h2>
        <p>
            Hi, I'm Eleni! Welcome to my blog where I share my passion for health, delicious food, and natural living.
            Eleni's Healthy Habits is your go-to resource for learning about nutritious ingredients, discovering the
            best organic products, and exploring vibrant farmers' markets.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
        <h3>Our Mission</h3>
        <p>
            At Eleni's Healthy Habits, we believe that good health starts with what you put on your plate. Our mission
            is to inspire you to make healthier choices by providing you with valuable insights, delicious recipes, and
            tips on incorporating wholesome ingredients into your daily routine.
        </p>

        <h3>Health Prompts and Tips</h3>
        <p>
            Explore our health prompts section where you can find daily tips and inspiration to help you stay on track
            with your wellness goals. From mindfulness practices to fitness routines, we've got you covered!
        </p>

        <h3>Good Food and Ingredient Options</h3>
        <p>
            Discover the best foods to fuel your body! We highlight a variety of nutritious ingredients, provide
            in-depth information about their health benefits, and share mouth-watering recipes that are easy to prepare
            and delightful to eat.
        </p>

        <h3>Organic and Bio Products</h3>
        <p>
            Navigating the world of organic products can be overwhelming. Let us guide you through the best options
            available, from fresh produce to pantry staples. Learn about the benefits of choosing organic and how it
            can improve your overall health.
        </p>

        <h3>Market Discoveries</h3>
        <p>
            Join us as we explore various free markets and topic markets. We bring you stories from local farmers, tips
            on finding the freshest ingredients, and highlights of unique products that you won't find in regular
            grocery stores.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="conclusion-section">
        <h3>Join Our Community</h3>
        <p>
            Eleni's Healthy Habits is more than just a blog – it's a community of like-minded individuals who are
            passionate about health and wellness. Follow us on social media, subscribe to our newsletter, and become
            part of our journey towards a healthier, happier life.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

